name: Appsy
author: Maprinter Ltd

sections.description:
A plugin for wordpress of Appsy to insert the script with the project ID.
This plugin requires account in: https://appsy.app

You can read our terms of use and privacy policy here:
Terms of Use: https://appsy.app/en/terms
Privacy Policy: https://appsy.app/en/privacy
sections.installation:
This plugin requires account in: https://appsy.app
Please create an account to receive your project ID
